data.description: This is what Indiana living is all about! Welcome home to this spacious ranch that features an open floor plan, newer vinyl plank flooring, updated kitchen and so much more! Both bathrooms were recently remodeled giving a spa-like feel right at home. Enjoy watching Shriner Lake's July 4th fireworks from your 960 SF deck! You will be ready for winter with the newer 96% HE 2 stage smart home furnace. Property comes with channel access to Round Lake (part of the Tri-Lakes) for both fishing and skiing. This home offers so much... Don't pass it up!
